Edward Binns https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_Binns 0 Edward Binns (September 12, 1916 – December 4, 1990) was an American stage, film and television actor. He had a wide-spanning career in film and television, often portraying competent, hard working and purposeful characters in his various roles.
